<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_12" id="5v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_12_line_1574073206434_468">Hercʒog <expan>fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Oſterreich / <expan>Hercʒ<ex>og</ex></expan> <expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſi<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_12_r2l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute fürbraht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l4">vvie daʒ Jn etwıeuil habe vnd kauffmanſchaft ın <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>herſchäft<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l7">vnd <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan> aufgehalten vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_12_line_1574073295884_479">etlich die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey </ab></add> bekumert ſeẏ worden / Darümb ſo <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l8">wir cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen / <expan>VVılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l9">Mendell mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden dauon cʒureden / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l10">derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſell / darümb cʒu diſem mal an ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l11"><expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> werb / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade darẏnne <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l12">verhoren vnd Jm des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd Jn auch darümb <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l13">von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> <expan>vert<ex>igen</ex></expan> wolle / Als etc das <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_12_r2l14"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egıdij Anno Nono </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_12" id="5v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Osterreich,
                                <expan>hercz<ex>og</ex></expan>
<expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute fürbraht, wie daz in etwievil
                        habe und kauffmanschaft in <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>herschäft<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan> aufgehalten und <add>etlich die
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey</add> bekumert sey worden.
                        Darümb so <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesellen
                            <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendell mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden davon czureden. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz derselb
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell darümb czu disem mal an ewr
                                <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> werb von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade
                        darynne <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> verhoren und im des
                                <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und in auch darümb
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>vert<ex>igen</ex></expan> wolle, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii anno
                        nono.</ab>
</div>
